            var user = navigator.userAgent;

            /*IE11 timeout*/

            function stopMicroBrowser() {
                var  disableMicroBrowser = true || false;
                var hasPlatform = typeof window.platform !== 'undefined';
                var hasNavigator = typeof  navigator !== 'undefined';

                var uniqueTokensThatIdentifyInAppBrowsers = [
                        'FBAN',
                        'FBAV',
                        'Instagram',
                        'Twitter',
                        'MicroMessenger'
                    ];

                var getProduct = function getProduct() {
                    return hasPlatform && window.platform.product || hasNavigator && navigator.userAgent;
                };

                var getFamily = function getFamily() {
                    return hasPlatform && window.platform.os.family  || hasNavigator && navigator.userAgent;
                };

                var getUA = function getUA() {
                    return hasPlatform && window.platform.ua  || hasNavigator && navigator.userAgent;
                };

                var isOnMobileDevice = function isOnMobileDevice() {
                    return  getProduct().indexOf('iPhone') >= 0 || getFamily().indexOf('Android') >= 0
                };

                var isOnIpadDevice = function isOnIpadDevice() {
                    return getProduct().indexOf('iPad') >= 0;
                };

               var inAppBrowser = function inAppBrowser() {
                    var userAgent = getUA();
                    return uniqueTokensThatIdentifyInAppBrowsers.some(function(token){
                        return userAgent.indexOf(token) > -1;
                    });
                }
                var isOnDevice = isOnIpadDevice() || isOnMobileDevice();
                var block = inAppBrowser() && isOnDevice && disableMicroBrowser;
                if (block) {
                          var getDomain = function(win) {
                               return (window.location.protocol + '//' + window.location.hostname +
                                   (window.location.port ? ':' + window.location.port : '')).toLowerCase();
                           },
                           getOrigin = function() {
                               return window.document.location.origin || getDomain(window.document);
                           },
                           getParentDomain = function() {
                               const queryString = window.location.search;
                               const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(queryString);
                               return  urlParams.get('fromOrigin');
                           };
                           var childDomain = getOrigin();
                           var parentDomain =  getParentDomain();
                   
                           window.parent.postMessage ( { protocol: 'childEvent', command:  'error', domain: childDomain, data: { reason: 'stop' } } , parentDomain);
